ðŸ“¦ Key Components Overview

Folder/File	Purpose
core/	Django config and global URL routing
reminders/	Main logic for events, reminders, media, and UI
reminders/templates/	HTML templates (landing page, dashboard, celebration)
reminders/static/	CSS, JS, images, Lottie animations, fonts
reminders/serializers.py	DRF: Convert models to JSON for API
reminders/tasks.py	Scheduled email sending via Django Q
reminders/utils.py	Custom functions (SendGrid email, Supabase upload)
media/	Local uploads directory (for development)
requirements.txt	Python packages list
README.md	Project documentation